sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as API Server
    participant S as Service Layer
    participant R as Repository
    participant DB as Database

    C->>API: HTTP Request
    API->>S: DTO
    S->>R: Entity
    R->>DB: SQL Query
    DB-->>R: Result Set
    R-->>S: Entity
    S-->>API: DTO
    API-->>C: HTTP Response
